@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1

### Register new admin (creates User + Profile + Tenant "My Business")
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "owner@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

###

# @name login
### Login admin → captures token for downstream requests in this file
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "owner@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

###

### Login via Google ID token (paste credential from Google Sign-In)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/google/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "credential": "<google_id_token>"
}

###

### Current user
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me/
Authorization: Token {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### Complete onboarding (creates first store)
# code: ^[A-Z0-9]{3,10}$ — unique per tenant
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/onboarding/
Authorization: Token {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Toko Kelontong Pak Budi",
  "code": "TOKO01",
  "address": "Jl. Merdeka No. 10, Jakarta"
}

###

### Logout (deletes admin token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout/
Authorization: Token {{login.response.body.token}}
